Package: calypso
Title: The OMOP Data Catalogue Dashboard
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person('Milan', 'Malfait', email = 'm.malfait@ucl.ac.uk', role = c('cre', 'aut'))
Description: A Shiny app to display an OMOP data catalogue in an interactive dashboard. Enables
    users to interactively explore available OMOP concepts by displaying useful summary statistics
    and subsequently export a selection of concepts of interest.
